room_title: Escape room "The Heist" by ROOM 5280 in Seattle
room_description:
An eccentric millionaire has something that doesn’t belong to him. Your team is tasked to go in, find the items and extract them before anyone discovers you’re there. There is a problem though…

The greedy man has turned his house into a trap full of safes, locks and other “surprises”! Few would dare to go in… can your team pull off a perfect heist and escape?
